metadata.name: Aristocrats Battle #1
metadata.description:
BATTLE is a collection created by the modern French painter and a visionary,  Clément Mougel. 
All NFTs are unique and were assembled one by one to  by Clément. 
His artistic vision, distinct style and creativity are behind each piece!
Each NFT comes with its own print, numbered and signed. 
This limit edition is a true piece of art!
